      <p class="text-[#E7CE50]/90 text-lg mb-5">DVSA approved &bull; Male &amp; female instructors &bull; Est. 1998</p>
      <p class="text-white/80 mb-8">At Accelerate you can be sure to receive the best instructors available. We offer driving lessons, intensive courses, and semi-intensive courses covering Glasgow, Paisley, and all surrounding areas.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="tel:07397040400" class="bg-[#E7CE50] text-[#423F33] font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#B9A540] transition-colors">📞 07397 040400</a>
        <a href="/D1912/lessons-cost-glasgow" class="border-2 border-[#E7CE50] text-[#E7CE50] font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#E7CE50] hover:text-[#423F33] transition-colors">View Prices</a>
