    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Lessons offered -->
<section class="py-16 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#423F33] mb-3 text-center">What I Offer</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-[#8B7C30] mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">A Glasgow driving school offering a high quality service at very competitive prices. Fully qualified instructors working one to one with every pupil.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-[#F8F0CB] overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/D1912/images/school-of-motoring.png" alt="Standard driving lessons" width="291" height="220" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#423F33] text-xl mb-2">Standard Lessons</h3>
          <p class="text-[#8B7C30] text-sm mb-4">One-to-one tuition with a fully qualified DVSA instructor. We welcome nervous, young, and older drivers. Full hour guaranteed.</p>
          <a href="/D1912/lessons-cost-glasgow" class="text-[#B9A540] font-semibold text-sm hover:underline">View prices &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-[#F8F0CB] overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/D1912/images/driving-lessons-paisley.png" alt="Intensive driving courses" width="291" height="220" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#423F33] text-xl mb-2">Intensive Courses</h3>
          <p class="text-[#8B7C30] text-sm mb-4">Semi-intensive and full intensive courses available. Ideal if you have a test date booked or need to pass quickly.</p>
          <a href="/D1912/intensive-driving-courses" class="text-[#B9A540] font-semibold text-sm hover:underline">Learn more &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-[#F8F0CB] overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/D1912/images/accelerate-car-tuition.png" alt="Pass Plus Glasgow" width="291" height="220" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#423F33] text-xl mb-2">Pass Plus</h3>
          <p class="text-[#8B7C30] text-sm mb-4">Post-test training covering motorways, night driving, rural roads and dual carriageways. May reduce your insurance premium.</p>
          <a href="/D1912/pass-plus-glasgow" class="text-[#B9A540] font-semibold text-sm hover:underline">Find out more &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About Me -->
<section class="py-16 px-4 bg-[#FDFBF1]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div>
      <img src="/D1912/images/steven-love.png" alt="Steven Love, driving instructor" width="291" height="220" class="rounded-xl shadow-md w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#423F33] mb-5">About Me</h2>
      <p class="text-[#453E18] mb-4">Accelerate Driving Tuition was established in 1998 by myself, Steven Love. Having qualified as an instructor in 1996 and worked for two years for a reputable driving school, I built Accelerate with one goal: quality tuition and a professional service.</p>
      <p class="text-[#453E18] mb-4">I understand that each pupil is completely different and we all learn at different speeds. With this in mind I train each pupil to a very high standard, giving them the awareness and safety that will keep them safe on our roads for many years.</p>
      <p class="text-[#453E18] mb-6">We welcome nervous, young, and older drivers. Our aim is to teach safe driving for passing your test and beyond.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/D1912/about-us" class="bg-[#423F33] text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#35322A] transition-colors">Read More</a>
        <a href="tel:07397040400" class="border border-[#423F33] text-[#423F33] font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#423F33] hover:text-white transition-colors">Call Me</a>
