    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-10 text-center">Testimonials</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <p class="text-white/90 mb-5 italic text-sm">"Having passed my test first time with Accelerate Driving Tuition, I would have no problems recommending them to anyone wishing to take lessons. All my lessons went well and I was put at ease from the moment I got into the car."</p>
        <p class="text-[#E7CE50] font-bold">Alexander Paton</p>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">Lessons &bull; East Kilbride</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <p class="text-white/90 mb-5 italic text-sm">"I can only thank Accelerate for getting me, my wife and my son through the driving test. As soon as my daughter is seventeen I will be phoning to book her in for lessons."</p>
